			<h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://getglennmobile.com/2014/03/09/sorry-we-are-closed/" rel="bookmark">We Are CLOSED!</a></h2>	
	<div class="post-date">
		<p class="day"><a href="http://getglennmobile.com/2014/03/09/sorry-we-are-closed/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to We Are CLOSED!">Mar 9</a></p>
	</div><!-- .post-date -->

	<div class="post-info clear-block">
		<p class="author alignleft">Posted by <a href="http://getglennmobile.com/author/libertyonwheels/" title="Posts by Glenn Horowitz" rel="author">Glenn Horowitz</a></p>
	</div><!-- .post-info clear-block" -->

	<div class="entry clear-block">
		<p><a href="http://libertyonwheels.com/" target="_blank"><img class="decoded" alt="http://www.febland.co.uk/images/led046_led_closed_sign.jpg" src="http://www.febland.co.uk/images/led046_led_closed_sign.jpg" width="588" height="228" /></a></p>
<p>If there&#8217;s a shred of doubt, Get Glenn Mobile! is now CLOSED.</p>
<p>Please visit my new blog <a href="http://libertyonwheels.com/" target="_blank">Liberty On Wheels</a> if you&#8217;d like, or click on the image above.</p>
<p>Apart from that, nothing&#8217;s gonna happen here.</p>
			</div><!-- .entry -->

